seller.oneLinerTitle: I help people and businesses thrive
seller.description:
I help others get into alignment in their business and lives. I have an extensive background in spiritual and business strategies.

Business Strategies include SEO, social media, E-Commerce (including Etsy & Amazon), Niche Marketing, Marketing, Advertising & Branding.

The Spiritual Arts include Color therapy, the Law of Attraction, Crystals & Gemstones. 

My experience & background allows me to take an intuitive approach in life & business so you can thrive!

reviews.comment: Melissa is a gem.  It was an absolute pleasure working with her.  She reviewed and overhauled my Etsy store, and did research on and updated some Etsy listings.  She also provided guidance for future reference.  Melissa was communicative, kind, strategic in her research and execution, professional, and it's very clear that she's an Etsy expert and takes pride in her work. Should I require more help on my Etsy store, I must say honestly (despite the possibility that she won't be available if I need her services for Etsy again, because she'll be even busier now) that she will be my top choice to reach out to, without hesitation.  You'll be in great hands with Melissa.  It will take time to see how the updates to my Etsy store manifest, but regardless, I know she did her best work on my store.  She's also very responsive to follow-up questions, and provides meaningful responses.  One thing I would suggest to anyone who works with Melissa: help her help you.  Be communicative and answer her questions thoughtfully, particularly if you've asked for a store design or overhaul.  She curated those questions for a reason - to deliver her best work for you.  Thank you, Melissa.  It was an absolute pleasure working with you.  It's clear to me why you are Fiverr's Choice.  Best of luck with all you do.

Melissa was amazing! Not only did she deliver exactly what I was looking for but she was responsive, understanding and supportive. I am a brand new Etsy seller and because of her help I feel like my shop will actually start to get noticed the way I was hoping. 
She answered all my questions, and even extended the time line for delivery when I needed a few more days to get her what she needed. 
I am so happy with the way my shop looks now and I'm excited to see what the future holds as an Etsy seller.
I would highly recommend Melissa to anyone needing help with their Etsy store - whether they are a new seller (like me) or an experienced one that just needs a little updating!

I am a new Etsy seller and initially wasn't sure which gig was right for me. So, I briefly explained my situation and where I needed help. She recommended the audit and/or consultation. Eventually, I just ordered both and couldn't be happier. The audit was very detailed and tailored to my needs. It also included a few general tips and recommendations that are important for a new Etsy seller like me. For the follow-up video call consultation, I sent her my questions just 5 minutes beforehand, and she addressed all of them, even the spontaneous ones that came up. I would recommend Melissa's audit to any new Etsy seller and look forward to our continued collaboration!

Just got my new titles tags and descriptions for my Etsy item! They are not live in my shop! This was a great experience and I believe with this I will start to see many more customers come to my shop! When that happens I will be getting the rest of my shop revamped! 

Thank you so much!

Melissa went above and beyond with our service. We bought the premium package and she did an amazing job, we’re very happy and pleased with the finished product. Not only that she did an excellent job but she’s a true professional, she answered all of our questions and gave us several advices. We highly recommend her services. Will hire her again.
As always, great experience with mam. Thankyou for the tip mam.
Very humble and polite client easy to work with will love to work with you again.

She is Great and as always Outstanding Experience :)
Thank You so much for your order.
Great Communication. She always supports me throughout.

I would love to work with you again on another project and Thanks again for your order.
